text.tspan: Share of male vs female employment in agriculture, 2019
The horizontal axis shows female employment in agriculture as a share of total female employment. The vertical
axis shows male employment in agriculture as a share of total male employment. The agriculture sector consists of
activities in agriculture, hunting, forestry and fishing.
Employment in agriculture, female (% of female employment)
Employment in agriculture, male (% of male employment)
Source: International Labour Organization (via World Bank)
